KMCP.OL.summary: KMC Properties AS owns and operates industrial and logistic properties. KMC Properties AS was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Hammarvika, Norway.

NPRO.OL.summary: Norwegian Property ASA, a real estate investment company, acquires, develops, manages, and sells commercial real estate properties in Norway. Its properties primarily comprise office premises with associated warehousing and car parks, and retail and restaurant spaces. As of December 31, 2019, the company owned 28 office, commercial, and residential properties primarily in Oslo; and a development property at Forus in Stavanger. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Oslo, Norway. Norwegian Property ASA operates as a subsidiary of Geveran Trading Co Ltd.

S2B.F.summary: Selvaag Bolig ASA, a housing development company, engages in the development, construction, and sale of residential properties in Greater Oslo, Bergen, Stavanger, Trondheim, and Stockholm. The company offers its properties under the Start, Home, and Pluss brands. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Oslo, Norway. Selvaag Bolig ASA is a subsidiary of Selvaag AS.
